<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.6.5">
<l>iṭumpaiyā laṭarppuṇ ṭiṭumiṉō</l>
<l>tuṟṟeṉ ṟirantavark killaiyē yeṉṟu</l>
<l>neṭuñcolāl maṉutta nīcaṉē ṉantō</l>
<l>niṉaikkilēṉ viṉaippayaṉ taṉṉai</l>
<l>kaṭuñcolār kaṭiyār kālaṉār tamarāl</l>
<l>paṭuvatōr koṭumiṟaik kañci</l>
<l>naṭuṅkināṉ vantuṉ tiruvaṭi yaṭaintēṉ</l>
<l>naimicā raṇiyat tuḷentāy.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Vile me, who is shamed by [my] cruel word, “No” to those ruined by poverty</l>
<l rend="indent">who entreated, “Will you please give us rice?”</l>
<l>Sadly, I did not think of the outcome of [that] action.</l>
<l>Fearing for one brutal affliction, the suffering from the servants of Death,</l>
<l rend="indent">those of cruelty and those of cruel words,</l>
<l>Trembling, coming [here], I took refuge at your divine feet,</l>
<l rend="indent">my father in Naimiśāraṇyam.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
